  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Manage Your Operations</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build a strong fleet of vehicles to start your cargo operations. A fleet of bicycles and motorcycles that fit different delivery needs will meet all your needs. Also, a backpack will allow you to carry more cargo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't forget to add commercial vehicles to your fleet that will come with new updates, but you may need a driver's license. :)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757600/extras/4d65b2e495c62fe61730797268967b9b.avif?t=1770196958\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757600/extras_big/4d65b2e495c62fe61730797268967b9b.avif?t=1770196958 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong><i>Ensure Customer Satisfaction</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increase customer satisfaction by delivering fast and reliable cargo. Optimize delivery routes, deliver cargo at the right time. Gain customer trust and grow your business with effective cargo distribution strategies in My Corp Cargo Simulator!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757600/extras/641b1c26fcc66e1ec5a7421f39983d15.avif?t=1770196958\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757600/extras_big/641b1c26fcc66e1ec5a7421f39983d15.avif?t=1770196958 width=800 height=452 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Be Fast</i></strong>If you are running a cargo company, you need to be fast. Customers waiting in line will not make you money, they will only be annoying. Do the transactions of the customers quickly and distribute the cargo from street to street. Remember, the cargo empire you want to establish is waiting faster than you. You have no employees and no one to help you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757600/extras/82105d6d4b4446389f455c9b69565df8.avif?t=1770196958\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757600/extras_big/82105d6d4b4446389f455c9b69565df8.avif?t=1770196958 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Manage Your Operations</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build a strong fleet of vehicles to start your cargo operations. A fleet of bicycles and motorcycles that fit different delivery needs will meet all your needs. Also, a backpack will allow you to carry more cargo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't forget to add commercial vehicles to your fleet that will come with new updates, but you may need a driver's license. :)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757600/extras/4d65b2e495c62fe61730797268967b9b.avif?t=1770196958\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757600/extras_big/4d65b2e495c62fe61730797268967b9b.avif?t=1770196958 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong><i>Ensure Customer Satisfaction</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increase customer satisfaction by delivering fast and reliable cargo. Optimize delivery routes, deliver cargo at the right time. Gain customer trust and grow your business with effective cargo distribution strategies in My Corp Cargo Simulator!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757600/extras/641b1c26fcc66e1ec5a7421f39983d15.avif?t=1770196958\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757600/extras_big/641b1c26fcc66e1ec5a7421f39983d15.avif?t=1770196958 width=800 height=452 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Be Fast</i></strong>If you are running a cargo company, you need to be fast. Customers waiting in line will not make you money, they will only be annoying. Do the transactions of the customers quickly and distribute the cargo from street to street. Remember, the cargo empire you want to establish is waiting faster than you. You have no employees and no one to help you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757600/extras/82105d6d4b4446389f455c9b69565df8.avif?t=1770196958\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757600/extras_big/82105d6d4b4446389f455c9b69565df8.avif?t=1770196958 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
